    ### Mango Languages #{link_to "@", "http://mangolanguages.com", class: "right glow"}
    Mango Languages specializes in language learning software for consumers and libraries. I was contracted to create a **Google Hangout** application called Mango Skits; a multiplayer game to presented at **Google IO**.

    #### responsibilities
    * Deployed from initial concept to production **1 month before deadline**.
    * Built on **Heroku** and **Twitter Bootstrap** using **Ruby on Rails 3.2**.
    * Collaborated with **Google** to harness their immature API.

    ### SpeedySeat #{link_to "@", "http://speedyseat.us", class: "right glow"}
    A front-house restaurant reservation and seating system.

    #### responsibilities
    * Page creation with **Jade** templating and **Sass**.
    * Mobile optimization via **CSS media queries**.
    * Deployment via **Chef** to Amazon's **EC2** and **S3** cloud platform.

    #### accomplishments
    * Developed and deployed application to **3 restaurants in 3 months**.
    * Corrected cross-browser issues.
    * Deployed a rock solid **load balanced platform** for a **shared-nothing-architecture**.

    ### Nirrius #{link_to "@", "http://nirri.us", class: "right glow"}
    A complete server deployment and content management system implementation. Nirrius is #{link_to "open source", "https://github.com/nirrius/minecraft", target: "_blank"}.

    #### responsibilities
    * **RefineryCMS** front-end with blog engine and game server statistic integration.
    * Minecraft server deployment via **Xen Hypervisor** with **CraftBukkit server framework**.
    * Integrated billing system into game server software.

    #### accomplishments
    * Created a bustling community with over **1,000 invitation requests**.
    * Migrated systems to **Git revision control** for rapid deployment via **Xen**.
    * Project reached financial stability in just **3 months** and profits in just **6 months**.

    ### Redacted.io (beta) #{link_to "@", "http://redacted.io", class: "right glow"}
      
    Redacted.io is a managed server provider for zero-configuration deployment. Like #{link_to "Heroku", "http://heroku.com", target: "_blank"}, customers can host their favorite multiplayer games with little technical knowledge needed. This project is still in development.

    #### responsibilities
    * Built a **collocated** server designed for **reliable storage** and **scalability**.
    * Integrated **Ruby on Rails** front-end with **Sinatra** back-end.

    #### accomplishments
    * Bootstrapped company, moved from initial concept to **profits in 4 months**.
    * Designed and developed a commercial sales platform using **Ruby on Rails**.
    * Managed **Ubuntu Linux** servers running often immature game server software with **99+%** uptime.

